{"id":158225,"type":1,"name":"ガラスの城","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/17/d7/158225_M2hhH.jpg","summary":"ロザリンドはロンドンの博物館長を父に持つ8歳の美少女。その天使のような容姿と品のある仕草に誰もが彼女を愛してしまう。しかし彼女は実は母方の呪われた血を引く天性の殺人鬼だったのだ。ロザリンドは自分の宝物を増やすため、嘘つきをこらしめるため、時には人助けのため、次々と無邪気な殺戮を重ねていく。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>玻璃之城</li><li><span>册数: </span>8</li><li><span>作者: </span><a href=\"/person/21117\">わたなべまさこ</a></li><li><span>出版社: </span><a href=\"/person/1307\">集英社</a></li><li><span>连载杂志: </span><a href=\"/person/8685\">マーガレット</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>玻璃城</li><li><span>开始: </span>1969年3号</li><li><span>结束: </span>1970年49号</li>","collection":{"wish":6,"collect":1},"tags":[{"name":"百合","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":21117,"image":"","name":"渡边雅子","desc":"作者"},{"id":1307,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/84/0b/1307_prsn_4oZny.jpg","name":"集英社","desc":"出版社"},{"id":8685,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/19/3d/8685_prsn_bgDFG.jpg","name":"玛格丽特","desc":"连载杂志"}],"comic":[{"id":158217,"name":"ガラスの城 (1)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/0b/ac/158217_F3Cv0.jpg"},{"id":158218,"name":"ガラスの城 (2)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/94/58/158218_82888.jpg"},{"id":158219,"name":"ガラスの城 (3)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/2d/df/158219_KGKG0.jpg"},{"id":158220,"name":"ガラスの城 (4)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/75/b0/158220_89ImX.jpg"},{"id":158221,"name":"ガラスの城 (5)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/30/0f/158221_LmzTj.jpg"},{"id":158222,"name":"ガラスの城 (6)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/3d/c9/158222_HZzIT.jpg"},{"id":158223,"name":"ガラスの城 (7)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/d3/64/158223_wIwzX.jpg"},{"id":158224,"name":"ガラスの城 (8)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/6b/15/158224_6Ergg.jpg"}]}